OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy firms ordered to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcall struggling customers  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy firms have been told to contact 
OL,6, customers who miss payments as the     
OL,7, regulator cracks down on poor customer 
OL,8, service standards.                     
OL,10,FUnder Ofgem's rules taking effect on 14
OL,11,FDecember, suppliers must get in touch  
OL,12,Fwith customers who miss two monthly or 
OL,13,Fone quarterly payment to offer support.
OL,15,FThey have also been told to prioritise 
OL,16,Fvulnerable customers.                  
OL,18,FCustomer service scores must also be   
OL,19,Fpublished, in a scheme similar to that 
OL,20,Fused by banks.                         
